WEBVTT

00:04:28.490 --> 00:04:32.252
Well, once we had stopped
and stabilized the damage,

00:04:32.276 --> 00:04:33.809
it was no longer a red.

00:04:34.125 --> 00:04:35.791
It felt red,

00:04:35.815 --> 00:04:38.127
but it was in fact just noise.

00:04:38.543 --> 00:04:40.392
No, no really, it was quite noisy,

00:04:40.416 --> 00:04:43.196
this picture on the far right
is me wearing earplugs

00:04:43.220 --> 00:04:44.646
to focus on my book,

00:04:44.670 --> 00:04:47.756
while the floor is being
mechanically dried around me.

00:04:48.458 --> 00:04:50.315
Know your reds,

00:04:50.339 --> 00:04:54.140
and do not let your non-reds
distract you from them.

00:04:54.974 --> 00:04:57.688
By the way, it is liberating
with a green task

00:04:57.712 --> 00:05:00.256
to, every once in a while,
be able to remind yourself,